sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as React UI
  participant API as ResourceLibrary.API
  participant CQ as MediatR CQRS
  participant SVC as AiAudioService
  participant COQ as Coqui TTS

  UI->>API: POST /api/aiAudio/tts/coqui { text, voice, rate? }
  API->>CQ: SynthesizeWithCoquiCommand
  CQ->>SVC: SynthesizeWithCoquiAsync(text, voice, rate?)
  SVC->>COQ: POST /api/tts (JSON)
  COQ-->>SVC: audio/wav
  SVC-->>CQ: byte[]
  CQ-->>API: byte[] (WAV)
  API-->>UI: File(speech_coqui.wav)
